+# Local Beltrami Alignment And Its Hybrids Do Not Survive
+
+Status: `VERIFIED` with `INFERRED` route verdict
+
+Local Beltrami deficit or alignment collapses at the geometry Tao screen.
+
+The operative reason is structural:
+
+- exact Beltrami cancellation acts on the Lamb-vector or pressure-loss side
+  rather than directly on full stretching
+- small local Beltrami deficit does not by itself control `S omega`,
+  `S omega . omega`, or the exterior or nonlocal strain remainder
+
+Exploration 002 therefore classifies:
+
+- `local Beltrami deficit or alignment` as `collapsed to Tao-robust/static geometry`
+- `Beltrami deficit plus concentration` as only `weak but informative`
+- `Beltrami deficit plus anisotropy` as only `weak but informative`
+
+The hybrids do not rescue the route because concentration or anisotropy still
+has to be turned into a named reduction of the full stretching contribution,
+including the exterior field.
+
+Filed from:
+- `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-002-exploration-002-geometry-tao-screen.md`
