+  only counts candidates that move a full `S omega . omega` contribution rather
+  than a local proxy.
+- `local-beltrami-alignment-and-its-hybrids-do-not-survive.md`: Beltrami-first
+  routes collapse because they control the wrong quantity and leave nonlocal
+  strain live.
+- `standalone-direction-coherence-and-tube-persistence-remain-diagnostic.md`:
+  each surviving non-Beltrami family is informative, but neither is a live
+  standalone route on the current record.
+- `direction-coherence-plus-tube-persistence-is-the-only-live-geometry-survivor.md`:
+  the only Step-2 survivor is the dynamic hybrid combining a stretching-facing
+  observable with plausible NS-specific persistence.
