@@ -0,0 +1,23 @@
+# Direction Coherence Plus Tube Persistence Is The Only Live Geometry Survivor
+
+Status: `INFERRED` from verified screening constraints
+
+After the Step-2 Tao screen, the only primary survivor is the hybrid
+`direction coherence plus tube persistence`.
+
+This family remains live because it is the only locally suggested candidate
+that combines:
+
+- a stretching-facing observable
+- a plausible Navier-Stokes-specific persistence feature that Tao-style
+  averaging would plausibly destroy
+
+The route is still narrow. It is only justified if Step 2 chooses a scenario
+class and localization protocol that test one specific question:
+
+Can direction coherence persist along a coherent tube family strongly enough to
+make a full stretching contribution, including the exterior or inter-scale
+part, smaller in one fixed representation?
+
+Filed from:
+- `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-002-exploration-002-geometry-tao-screen.md`
