+# Standalone Direction Coherence And Tube Persistence Remain Diagnostic
+
+Status: `VERIFIED` with `INFERRED` screening verdict
+
+On the current repository record, the two non-Beltrami survivor families remain
+useful comparators but not live standalone routes:
+
+- `vorticity-direction coherence` is genuinely stretching-facing, but without a
+  new bridge from local coherence to a smaller full `S omega . omega` term it
+  mostly restates an existing direction-regularity orbit
+- `tube coherence or persistence` is the most plausible Tao-sensitive dynamic
+  ingredient, but tube imagery alone is descriptive unless it suppresses the
+  exterior or inter-scale stretching contribution or the localization-evolution
+  cost
+
+Exploration 002 therefore keeps both families as `weak but informative` rather
+than promoting either one as a primary Step-2 route.
+
+Filed from:
+- `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-002-exploration-002-geometry-tao-screen.md`
