+# Screen Geometry Branches For Full Stretching And Dynamic Content
+
+For geometry branches, do not let static geometry through the Tao screen.
+
+The candidate should survive only if its essential content is at least one of:
+
+- dynamic coherence
+- persistence under transport or multiscale evolution
+- a true algebraic link to full stretching
+
+Treat the following as dead unless they are upgraded to a full-stretching gain:
+
+- static alignment or anisotropy language
+- pure concentration descriptions
+- control of `u x omega` without control of `S omega . omega`
+
+Filed from:
